RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

93-1098. State v. Gill.

Franklin County, No. 92AP-945. Reported at 70 Ohio St.3d 150, 637 N.E.2d 897. On motion for reconsideration by appellant, motion for reconsideration by appellee, and on amicus curiae motion for leave to file under S.Ct.Prac.R. XI by Central Ohio Association of Criminal Defense Lawyers. Motions denied.

Wright and Pfeifer, JJ., dissent. Resnick, J., not participating.
